msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/date"
msgid "31st August, 1941 · Ino, Finland"
msgstr "31 de agosto de 1941 - Ino, Finlandia"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/men"
msgid "You lost all your men!"
msgstr "¡Has perdido a todos tus hombres!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/name"
msgid "Stalin's Big Guns"
msgstr "Las grandes armas de Stalin"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/name_big"
msgid "Stalin's Big Guns"
msgstr "Las grandes armas de Stalin"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/01"
msgid ""
"Soldiers, the enemy is retreating, but our air force has informed us that "
"their progress has come to a halt. This is a great opportunity to seize a "
"vital piece of equipment and turn the tide of the war!"
msgstr ""
"Soldados, el enemigo se está retirando, pero nuestra fuerza aérea nos ha "
"informado de que su progreso se ha detenido. ¡Esta es una gran oportunidad "
"para apoderarse de una pieza vital del equipo y cambiar el rumbo de la "
"guerra!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/02"
msgid ""
"Your objective today is to capture a set of soviet long range railway gun! "
"Move northward through the woods until you reach the railway tracks and "
"await further instructions!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tu objetivo hoy es capturar un conjunto de cañones de ferrocarril "
"soviéticos de largo alcance! ¡Avanza hacia el norte por el bosque hasta "
"llegar a las vías del tren y espera más instrucciones!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/03"
msgid ""
"Avoid unnecessary engagements with the enemy. We do not have the manpower to "
"spare. Stick to the point!"
msgstr ""
"Evite los enfrentamientos innecesarios con el enemigo. No nos sobra el "
"personal. ¡Ve al grano!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/04"
msgid ""
"Right, we have located the railway gun following the railway tracks to the "
"east! It seems they are attempting to sabotage it to avoid capture. One of "
"the railway guns has already been blown up! Quickly, overwhelm the enemy and "
"take control of the last remaining gun!"
msgstr ""
"Bien, ¡hemos localizado el cañón del ferrocarril siguiendo las vías del tren "
"hacia el este! Parece que están intentando sabotearlo para evitar su "
"captura. ¡Uno de los cañones del ferrocarril ya ha sido volado! ¡Rápido, "
"abrumad al enemigo y tomad el control del último cañón que queda!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/05"
msgid ""
"Good job, the gun is in our hands. Thankfully, it comes in loaded with "
"ammunition. "
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, el arma está en nuestras manos. Afortunadamente, viene cargada "
"de munición. "

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/06"
msgid ""
"Now we need to securely evacuate the gun, but the enemy presence in the "
"village is threatening the operation. We need you to drive the Soviets off "
"this settlement. Use any means necessary, flatten that village to the ground "
"if you need to!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora tenemos que evacuar el cañón de forma segura, pero la presencia "
"enemiga en el pueblo amenaza la operación. Necesitamos que expulses a los "
"soviéticos de este asentamiento. Usa cualquier medio necesario, ¡aplasta esa "
"aldea hasta el suelo si es necesario!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/07"
msgid ""
"The enemy seems to be unhappy with the loss of their railway gun. Our "
"observers have picked up an enemy column moving this way to take their asset "
"back. It is imperative you hold your position and prevent the enemy from "
"destroying the gun."
msgstr ""
"El enemigo parece estar descontento con la pérdida de su cañón ferroviario. "
"Nuestros observadores han detectado una columna enemiga moviéndose en esta "
"dirección para recuperar su activo. Es importante que mantengan su posición "
"y eviten que el enemigo destruya el cañón."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/08"
msgid ""
"I am dispatching additional reinforcements to bolster your defensive "
"capabilities."
msgstr ""
"Estoy enviando refuerzos adicionales para reforzar tus capacidades "
"defensivas."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/09"
msgid "The enemy column has arrived! Wipe them out, all of them!"
msgstr "¡La columna enemiga ha llegado! ¡Acabad con ellos, con todos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/10"
msgid ""
"The enemy is launching an amphibious assault on the southern coastline! Get "
"to the beach and eliminate their landing crafts!"
msgstr ""
"¡El enemigo está lanzando un asalto anfibio en la costa sur! ¡Llega a la "
"playa y elimina sus embarcaciones!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/narrator/officer/secret"
msgid "Well, well, what have we here? It seems the soviets lost something."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, bueno, ¿qué tenemos aquí? Parece que los soviéticos perdieron algo."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"You’ve done it! We now have two heavy artillery pieces and a trainload of "
"ammo on top of that. This is a big result, promotion can’t be too far away "
"for you now. The railway guns will be towed to our lines tomorrow, and it "
"won’t take long before we’ll be able to use them against the previous "
"owners. Great job!"
msgstr ""
"¡Lo has conseguido! Ahora tenemos dos piezas de artillería pesada y un tren "
"cargado de munición. Este es un gran resultado, el ascenso no puede estar "
"muy lejos para ti ahora. Los cañones del ferrocarril serán remolcados a "
"nuestras líneas mañana, y no tardaremos en poder utilizarlos contra los "
"anteriores propietarios. ¡Gran trabajo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This is quite a blow. We have missed the opportunity to seize heavy "
"weaponry, let’s hope the enemy won’t deploy it against us. They might re- "
"deploy the railway guns in support of their own fortified line, 30 "
"kilometres south- east of here. We have to try again for sure, there is no "
"way around that, or the entire strategic plan is compromised!"
msgstr ""
"Esto es un gran golpe. Hemos perdido la oportunidad de apoderarnos de "
"armamento pesado, esperemos que el enemigo no lo despliegue contra nosotros. "
"Podrían volver a desplegar los cañones del ferrocarril en apoyo de su propia "
"línea fortificada, a 30 kilómetros al sureste de aquí. Tenemos que "
"intentarlo de nuevo con seguridad, no hay manera de evitarlo, ¡o todo el "
"plan estratégico estará comprometido!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/place"
msgid "4th Army Corps"
msgstr "4º Cuerpo de Ejército"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/story"
msgid " The Finnish army is advancing towards Leningrad. At Ino station, Soviet troops are stranded because the railroad is blocked by a sabotaged locomotive. Among the stranded units are two railway guns and crew. They are supposed to withdraw from the front, but their movement orders have arrived too late. Then, the Finns arrive, and the station becomes the scene of a bitter struggle.\n\n In this mission, you will be in charge of the attack. Use your tactical skill to break the Soviet defensive perimeter. Make sure you take those railway guns intact, we could use them very well!"
msgstr ""
"El ejército finlandés avanza hacia Leningrado. \n"
"\n"
"En la estación de Ino, las tropas soviéticas están varadas porque el \n"
"\n"
"ferrocarril está bloqueado por una locomotora saboteada. Entre las \n"
"\n"
"unidades varadas hay dos cañones ferroviarios y su tripulación. \n"
"\n"
"Se supone que deben retirarse del frente, pero sus \n"
"\n"
"órdenes de movimiento han llegado demasiado tarde. \n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Entonces, los finlandeses llegan, y la estación se convierte \n"
"\n"
"el escenario de una amarga lucha. \n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"En esta misión, estarás a cargo del ataque. \n"
"\n"
"Usa tu habilidad táctica para romper el perímetro defensivo soviético. \n"
"\n"
"Asegúrate de tomar los cañones del ferrocarril intactos, \n"
"\n"
"¡podríamos darles un buen uso!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/task1"
msgid "Push inland towards the railway line"
msgstr "Empujar hacia el interior en dirección a la línea de ferrocarril"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/task2"
msgid "Drive the enemy off the railway and capture the remaining railway gun."
msgstr ""
"Expulsa al enemigo de la vía férrea y captura el cañón ferroviario restante."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/task3"
msgid "Drive the soviets from the village with the help of the railway gun."
msgstr ""
"Expulsa a los soviéticos de la aldea con la ayuda del cañón ferroviario."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/task4"
msgid "Defend the railway gun from any enemy counter-attacks."
msgstr "Defiende el cañón del ferrocarril de cualquier contraataque enemigo."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin/1941_08_ino_station/task5"
msgid "Defeat the enemy amphibious attack."
msgstr "Derrota el ataque anfibio enemigo."
